   A little trick to help protect you and your warder from this spell is to cast FF on yourself/warder before buffing.  What this will do is create a single empty slot as the first buff.  When someone/something does cancel magic on you or your warder, it hits an empty slot.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
